name: Enter Valid Date Range for Out Duty/Tour

testSteps.description: 1: Enter Valid Date Range for Out Duty/Tour ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=View Request Status, tab=Out Duty/Tour, dateRange=01 Apr 2022 - 31 Mar 2023})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "View Request Status" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
Then Verify Date Range field is present
Then Enter "01 Apr 2022 - 31 Mar 2023" "Valid" Date range
And Verify "01 Apr 2022 - 31 Mar 2023" text displays
Then Verify "01 Apr 2022 - 31 Mar 2023" is selected
